preferredLayoutSize(Container) - Method in class org.qsari.effectopedia.gui.comp.ExtendedScrollPaneLayout
The preferred size of a PathwaySpaceScrollPane is the size of the insets, plus the preferred size of the viewport, plus the preferred size of the visible headers and footers, plus the preferred size of the scrollbars that will appear given the current view and the current scrollbar displayPolicies.
